#!/bin/bash

cat << 'EOF'
ORGMODE HOTKEYS (nvim-orgmode)

HEADINGS
───────────────────────────────────
New heading below    <Leader>Enter
Promote heading      <<
Demote heading       >>
Next heading         }
Previous heading     {
Fold/unfold          Tab
Fold/unfold all      Shift+Tab

TODO STATES
───────────────────────────────────
Cycle state          cit
  (unmarked → TODO → DONE → unmarked)

CHECKBOXES
───────────────────────────────────
Toggle checkbox      Ctrl+Space
New checkbox below   <Leader>Enter  (on a checkbox line)

AGENDA & CAPTURE
───────────────────────────────────
Open agenda          <Leader>oa
Quick capture        <Leader>oc

LINES
───────────────────────────────────
Move line down       <Leader>j
Move line up         <Leader>k
EOF
